## Conventions (Summary)

- NO technical suffixes (`ProductNotFound`, not `ProductNotFoundException`)
- Value Objects ALWAYS, with `Supported` enum for validation
- NO static constants in VOs — use factory methods
- AssertJ always, Object Mother for test data, ElementPicker for random()
- NO tests for Value Objects or equals/hashCode
- Methods ≤20 lines, classes ≤200 lines, constructor injection only
- CQRS: Commands for writes, Queries for reads, DomainEvents for pub/sub

